<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TrueVow Profitability & ROI Comparison | Why $29 Beats $5,900 Salaries</title>
    <meta name="description" content="See exactly how TrueVow outruns in-house intake salaries, answering services, and DIY voicemail. Compare costs, run the ROI calculator, and prove the business case in minutes.">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="../assets/logo.svg">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #0A2463;
            --secondary: #D6A657;
            --slate-900: #0F172A;
            --slate-700: #334155;
            --slate-500: #64748B;
            --emerald-500: #10B981;
            --rose-500: #E11D48;
            --bg-light: #F8FAFC;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            color: #1A1A1A;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        nav {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 16px 0;
        }

        .nav-inner {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 24px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 60px;
            align-items: center;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover,
        .nav-links a[aria-current="page"] {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .nav-cta {
            margin-left: auto;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .nav-cta:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(10, 36, 99, 0.18);
        }

        .hero {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 18% -10%, rgba(214,166,87,0.25), transparent 58%),
                        linear-gradient(135deg, #010203, #101F3C 55%, #091020 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 90px 24px 90px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.1rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.18rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
            max-width: 760px;
            margin: 0 auto 32px;
        }

        .hero-highlight {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .metric-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 48px;
        }

        .metric-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 28px 24px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .metric-card h3 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .metric-card span {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
        }

        .section {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 90px 24px 60px;
        }

        .section h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--slate-900);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .section p.lead {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--slate-500);
            font-size: 1rem;
            max-width: 720px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
        }

        .comparison-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);
            border-radius: 18px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #FFFFFF;
        }

        .comparison-table thead {
            background: #F8FAFC;
        }

        .comparison-table th,
        .comparison-table td {
            padding: 22px 26px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 0.97rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E8F0;
        }

        .comparison-table th {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--slate-700);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        }

        .truevow-column {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F0F7FF, #FFFFFF);
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .option-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            background: rgba(10,36,99,0.1);
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
        }

        .cost-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 32px;
        }

        .cost-card {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;
            padding: 26px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .cost-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--slate-900);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .cost-card .amount {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .cost-card ul {
            list-style: none;
            color: var(--slate-500);
            font-size: 0.93rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .divider {
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(15,23,42,0.12), transparent);
            margin: 70px auto;
            max-width: 580px;
        }

        .calculator {
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 24px;
            border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;
            padding: 36px 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .calc-inputs label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--slate-700);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.4px;
        }

        .calc-inputs input[type="number"],
        .calc-inputs input[type="range"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #CBD5F5;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--slate-900);
        }

        .calc-inputs .range-value {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .calc-results {
            background: #0B1120;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 30px 26px;
            display: grid;
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .result-label {
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            opacity: 0.65;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .result-value {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .result-subtext {
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
        }

        .highlight-box {
            background: #ECFEF4;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--emerald-500);
            padding: 22px 26px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            font-size: 0.96rem;
            color: var(--slate-700);
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .alt-savings {
            display: grid;
            gap: 18px;
            margin-top: 32px;
        }

        .alt-row {
            background: #F8FAFC;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 18px 20px;
            border: 1px dashed rgba(15,23,42,0.12);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 4px;
        }

        .alt-row strong {
            color: var(--slate-900);
        }

        .cta-panel {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A2463, #081737);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 48px 32px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 32px 60px rgba(10,36,99,0.18);
        }

        .cta-panel h3 {
            font-size: 2.4rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .cta-panel p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
            max-width: 720px;
            margin: 0 auto 26px;
        }

        .cta-panel a {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 16px 34px;
            background: #FACC15;
            color: #1A1A1A;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-radius: 999px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(250,204,21,0.28);
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
        }

        .cta-panel a:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(250,204,21,0.35);
        }

        footer {
            background: #1A1A1A;
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 20px 120px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        footer .footer-inner {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        footer p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #999;
        }

        footer .footer-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 32px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            max-width: 900px;
        }

        footer .footer-grid h4 {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }

        footer .footer-grid a {
            color: #999;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        footer .footer-grid a:hover {
            color: white;
        }

        footer .legal-links {
            margin-top: 40px;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        footer .disclaimer {
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.7;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 32px auto 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 960px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .metric-card h3 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .calculator {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 720px) {
            .nav-links {
                display: none;
            }

            .hero {
                padding-top: 96px;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            .hero-highlight {
                display: block;
                border-radius: 16px;
                padding: 16px 20px;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }

            .comparison-table th,
            .comparison-table td {
                padding: 18px 16px;
            }

            .cta-panel h3 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-inner">
            <a href="/marketing/index.html" class="nav-logo">
                <img src="/assets/logo.svg" alt="TrueVow" />
            </a>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/marketing/index.html">Home</a>
                <a href="/marketing/how-it-works.html">How It Works</a>
                <a href="/marketing/pricing.html">Pricing</a>
                <a href="/marketing/county-cap.html">33% Cap</a>
                <a href="/marketing/profitability.html">ROI</a>
            </div>
            <a href="/marketing/apply.html" class="nav-cta">Apply Now &rarr;</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <h1>Become the Category Hero</h1>
        <p>Law firms like Peterson &amp; Rivera didn’t ask for “better Google Ads.” They wanted to be the firm every insurer fears because every intake is bullet-proof, auditable, and profitable. This page shows you how to prove that future with hard numbers.</p>
        <div class="hero-highlight">⚖️ Manual intake costs $910 per retained client vs $64 with TrueVow — keep the $846 difference</div>

        <div class="metric-row">
            <div class="metric-card">
                <h3>$910 vs $64</h3>
                <span>Manual receptionist cost per retained client vs. TrueVow. That’s $846 you keep every time you win.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-card">
                <h3>$12,845 / mo</h3>
                <span>Revenue recaptured by answering in 59 seconds instead of 2.7 hours (2.3 retained cases × $5,150).</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-card">
                <h3>11 free + $29</h3>
                <span>First 11 qualified bookings are on us. After that, you invest $29 only when a lead books with you.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="section" id="calculator" style="padding-bottom: 40px;">
        <h2>Model Your Own Unit Economics</h2>
        <p class="lead">Plug your marketing spend into our live calculator and watch the cost per retained client collapse. No email required—just the numbers your managing partner wants.</p>
        <div class="calculator" id="roiCalculator">
            <div class="calc-inputs">
                <label for="calcBookings">Qualified bookings per year</label>
                <input id="calcBookings" type="range" min="12" max="120" step="6" value="48" oninput="updateCalculator()">
                <div class="range-value"><span id="calcBookingsValue">48</span> bookings</div>

                <label for="calcManualCpa" style="margin-top:24px;">Current cost per booking</label>
                <input id="calcManualCpa" type="number" min="200" max="3000" step="10" value="910" oninput="updateCalculator()">
                <div class="range-value">Includes ad spend + staff screening</div>

                <label for="calcNetValue" style="margin-top:24px;">Net revenue per retained case</label>
                <input id="calcNetValue" type="number" min="1000" max="10000" step="50" value="5150" oninput="updateCalculator()">
                <div class="range-value">ABA 2024 solo PI average: $5,150</div>
            </div>

            <div class="calc-results">
                <div>
                    <div class="result-label">Annual spend (status quo)</div>
                    <div class="result-value" id="calcManualSpend">$43,680</div>
                    <div class="result-subtext">Bookings × current cost per booking</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="result-label">Annual spend (TrueVow)</div>
                    <div class="result-value" id="calcTruevowSpend">$1,392</div>
                    <div class="result-subtext">Bookings × $29</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="result-label">Annual savings</div>
                    <div class="result-value" id="calcSavings">$42,288</div>
                    <div class="result-subtext">Reinvest into more ads—or take as owner profit</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="result-label">Projected net revenue unlocked</div>
                    <div class="result-value" id="calcRevenue">$85,200</div>
                    <div class="result-subtext">Bookings × retained rate (39%) × net revenue/case</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-box" style="margin-top: 24px; max-width: 960px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
            <strong>Need help?</strong> Apply for the Founding Member program and we’ll complete the ROI workbook with your own funnel data during onboarding.
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="comparison">
        <h2>Marketing ROI &amp; Cost Per Acquisition</h2>
        <p class="lead">Solo and small firms routinely pay <strong>$500–$1,200</strong> to acquire a single client, while raw personal injury leads cost <strong>$150–$500+</strong>. The hidden bill arrives after the click: staff time rejecting 80% of the intake. TrueVow flips that equation so you only pay for the qualified bookings that create revenue.</p>

        <div class="highlight-box" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
            <strong>The waste inside the current funnel:</strong>
            <ul style="margin-top: 12px; padding-left: 18px; line-height: 1.6;">
                <li><strong>Manual screening:</strong> 7–10 minutes per lead = <strong>$8–$12</strong> of salary/benefits.</li>
                <li><strong>Attorney conflict check:</strong> another <strong>$25–$50</strong> of non-billable time.</li>
                <li><strong>Opportunity cost:</strong> viable calls are missed while staff reject the 80% that cannot be accepted.</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-top: 12px;">A $50 lead rapidly becomes a <strong>$83–$112</strong> expense before anyone says, “We can’t help you.” Multiply that across hundreds of PPC clicks and the math destroys profitability.</p>
        </div>

        <table class="comparison-table" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Current Intake Funnel</th>
                    <th>Cost Impact</th>
                    <th>Result</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Marketing vendor delivers a raw lead (PPC, LSA, SEO).</td>
                    <td>$150–$500+ per click/lead depending on practice area.</td>
                    <td>Cost incurred instantly—even if the lead is wrong practice, expired statute, or spam.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Intake specialist spends 7–10 minutes qualifying and rejecting.</td>
                    <td>$8–$12 of salary and benefits.</td>
                    <td>Non-billable overhead; morale drops with high rejection volume.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Attorney or paralegal confirms conflicts or requests documents.</td>
                    <td>$25–$50 of lost billable time.</td>
                    <td>Qualified pay work is delayed while the team cleans the pipeline.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Another ad click rings while staff are occupied.</td>
                    <td>$0 paid to vendor… but the potential client hires a competitor.</td>
                    <td>Revenue loss that never appears on a balance sheet.</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 20px;">Side-by-Side Cost Comparison</h2>
        <p class="lead">TrueVow converts unpredictable variable costs into a clean unit cost per qualified booking. You can finally scale marketing spend with confidence because the acquisition math is fixed.</p>
        <table class="comparison-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Option</th>
                    <th>Monthly Cost</th>
                    <th>Hidden or Opportunity Cost</th>
                    <th class="truevow-column">Conversion & ROI</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <span class="option-badge">TrueVow</span><br>
                        Pay per qualified consult only.
                    </td>
                    <td class="truevow-column">$0 base<br>$232 average (8 bookings × $29)</td>
                    <td>No payroll tax, benefits, or after-hours staffing. No charges for spam or expired statutes.</td>
                    <td class="truevow-column">68% consult-to-case rate (only qualified leads). Break-even after 1 retained case/month.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <span class="option-badge" style="background:rgba(239,68,68,0.1);color:#B91C1C;">In-House Intake Hire</span><br>
                        Salary + benefits + training.
                    </td>
                    <td>$4,850 salary<br>$1,100 benefits & payroll tax<br>$600 training → <strong>$6,550</strong></td>
                    <td>40-hour coverage only. Vacation, churn, HR liability. After-hours calls still missed.</td>
                    <td>42% conversion (unqualified calls). Needs 6 cases/month just to break even.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <span class="option-badge" style="background:rgba(245,158,11,0.18);color:#A16207;">24/7 Answering Service</span><br>
                        Per-minute billing.
                    </td>
                    <td>$1.75/min × 1,200 min = $2,100<br>+$150 transfers + $99 recording storage → <strong>$2,349</strong></td>
                    <td>Charges for spam. Agents read scripts, rarely qualify. Voicemail hand-offs at night.</td>
                    <td>31% conversion. Still spends 10+ hours/week calling back dead leads.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <span class="option-badge" style="background:rgba(59,130,246,0.18);color:#1D4ED8;">Generic AI Chat Widget</span><br>
                        Subscription + setup.
                    </td>
                    <td>$399/month subscription<br>$1,500–$3,000 setup<br>+$0.06/message overage</td>
                    <td>70% visitor drop-off. No voice. No calendaring. Sends partial data → staff chases.</td>
                    <td>12–18% conversion. Needs volume to justify. High brand risk for hallucinations.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <span class="option-badge" style="background:rgba(148,163,184,0.24);color:#475569;">Status Quo</span><br>
                        Voicemail + call backs.
                    </td>
                    <td>$0 direct spend</td>
                    <td>62% of callers never leave voicemail. 67% of after-hours calls missed. 12 hours/week wasted on dead leads.</td>
                    <td>2.5 retained cases/month average. Opportunity cost ≈ $154,500/year.</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <div class="highlight-box" style="margin-top:32px;">
            ⚖️ <strong>Key takeaway:</strong> The only line item you can fully control is cost-per-booking. TrueVow makes it a variable expense that scales with real revenue instead of fixed overhead.
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <section class="section" id="cost-breakdown">
        <h2>All-In Monthly Economics</h2>
        <p class="lead">Budget conversations crash when hidden expenses appear. Here’s what partners really pay once taxes, benefits, overtime, or missed calls are accounted for.</p>

        <div class="cost-grid">
            <div class="cost-card" style="background:#ECFEF4;border-color:#BBF7D0;">
                <h3>TrueVow (Pay-Per-Win)</h3>
                <div class="amount">$232</div>
                <ul>
                    <li>8 qualified bookings × $29 average.</li>
                    <li>0% charged on spam, wrong practice area, or expired cases.</li>
                    <li>24/7 coverage included (nights, weekends, Spanish).</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="cost-card">
                <h3>Intake Coordinator Salary</h3>
                <div class="amount">$6,550</div>
                <ul>
                    <li>$58,000 salary + 22% benefits + 1.5% payroll tax.</li>
                    <li>Recruiting & turnover: average 6 months ramp.</li>
                    <li>Still need after-hours answering (additional vendor).</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="cost-card">
                <h3>Answering Service</h3>
                <div class="amount">$2,349</div>
                <ul>
                    <li>1,200 billable minutes + transfer fees + storage.</li>
                    <li>Calls handed back to you for qualification.</li>
                    <li>No intake automation, no scheduling, no liability screening.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="cost-card">
                <h3>Doing Nothing</h3>
                <div class="amount" style="color:var(--rose-500);">$12,845 loss</div>
                <ul>
